### **4. 32_StreamPulseView**  
**Описание:**  
Плавный, живой график для визуализации потоков числовых данных в реальном времени.

#### `README.md`
```markdown
# StreamPulseView - Realtime Data Flow Visualizer

StreamPulseView displays incoming metric streams in a smooth, continuously updating chart view.

## Features
- Real-time scrolling  
- Refresh control  
- Built on Matplotlib

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/32_StreamPulseView.git
cd 32_StreamPulseView
python visualize.py
